# NOTE: gitignore is layered. This root file applies repo-wide; the
# subtree-merged webapp/ has its own webapp/.gitignore with additional
# rules (notably `*.md` to keep agent role docs out of git). When in doubt
# run `git check-ignore -v <path>` to see which file matched.

target
